Quick Tips

Grouping is available in the Columns tab by dragging the column name into the Row Groups section.

Sort any column by clicking on the column header. Click the column header again to change the sort order.

Expand or collapse row groups by right-clicking on a group header.

Adjust your column widths by dragging the divider bar to change single columns or clicking on the column menu (icon with three lines) and selecting Autosize or Resize to Fit to change all columns.

Open a link in a new hidden tab by holding the CTRL or CMD key while clicking on the link.
